---
/**
 * ContentReadme.astro — Tab "README.md": Ringkasan profesional
 *
 * Menampilkan profil Rico dalam gaya dokumen README yang di-render di editor kode.
 * Konten dalam Bahasa Inggris, bergaya terminal/markdown.
 *
 * Bagian-bagian:
 *   - Judul utama + paragraf pembuka
 *   - "What I Do" — layanan/keahlian utama
 *   - "Why Work With Me?" — alasan memilih Rico
 *   - Penutup / call to action
 */
---

<!-- Artikel README bergaya dokumen markdown di dalam editor kode -->
<article class="font-mono text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-300 max-w-none">

    <!-- ── Judul utama ───────────────────────────────────────────
         Ditulis besar dan berwarna accent, seperti heading H1 di README
         ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-5 leading-snug">
        Let's Build Quality Products Together
    </h1>

    <!-- ── Paragraf pembuka ──────────────────────────────────────
         Ringkasan singkat tentang Rico dan apa yang ditawarkan
         ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
    <p class="mb-8 text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
        With 5+ years of experience in QA engineering and project management, I help teams
        ship digital products that work — reliably, on time, and with full documentation.
        From structured test plans and API validation to end-to-end project delivery across
        mobile and web.
    </p>

    <!-- ── What I Do ────────────────────────────────────────────
         Daftar keahlian utama dengan nama tebal + deskripsi di bawahnya
         ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
    <h2 class="text-base font-bold text-primary mb-4">What I Do</h2>

    <!-- Daftar layanan — setiap item punya nama tebal dan deskripsi satu baris -->
    <ul class="mb-8 flex flex-col gap-3">

        <!-- Item: QA & Testing -->
        <li>
            <p class="text-gray-100 font-semibold before:content-['•'] before:mr-2 before:text-primary">
                Quality Assurance &amp; Testing
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-500 ml-4">
                Functional, regression, and E2E testing across mobile apps, web platforms, and CMS.
            </p>
        </li>

        <!-- Item: Project Management -->
        <li>
            <p class="text-gray-100 font-semibold before:content-['•'] before:mr-2 before:text-primary">
                Project Management
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-500 ml-4">
                End-to-end delivery — from FSD/SoW documentation to UAT sign-off and post-launch QA.
            </p>
        </li>

        <!-- Item: API Testing -->
        <li>
            <p class="text-gray-100 font-semibold before:content-['•'] before:mr-2 before:text-primary">
                API Testing &amp; Bug Tracking
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-500 ml-4">
                Postman for API validation, Hopscotch for manual testing, structured bug triage.
            </p>
        </li>

        <!-- Item: Stakeholder Communication -->
        <li>
            <p class="text-gray-100 font-semibold before:content-['•'] before:mr-2 before:text-primary">
                Stakeholder Communication
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-500 ml-4">
                Cross-functional coordination with clients, developers, and business teams.
            </p>
        </li>

        <!-- Item: Documentation -->
        <li>
            <p class="text-gray-100 font-semibold before:content-['•'] before:mr-2 before:text-primary">
                Documentation &amp; User Manuals
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-500 ml-4">
                Clear, structured docs — test cases, user manuals, QA guides, and technical reports.
            </p>
        </li>

    </ul>

    <!-- ── Why Work With Me? ─────────────────────────────────────
         Fakta dan nilai jual yang membedakan Rico dari kandidat lain
         ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
    <h2 class="text-base font-bold text-primary mb-4">Why Work With Me?</h2>

    <!-- Daftar poin keunggulan -->
    <ul class="mb-10 flex flex-col gap-2">
        {[
            '300+ test cases executed across 6 enterprise product cycles.',
            'Managed 15+ projects for clients including Danone, Bayer, PT Astra Digital, and PT Kalbe Farma.',
            'Comfortable on both sides — technical QA depth and strategic project oversight.',
            'Detail-oriented, async-friendly, and documentation-first in every engagement.',
        ].map(point => (
            <!-- Setiap poin diawali bullet • warna putih -->
            <li class="text-gray-400 before:content-['•'] before:mr-2 before:text-gray-100">
                {point}
            </li>
        ))}
    </ul>

    <!-- ── Garis pemisah sebelum penutup ─────────────────────── -->
    <hr class="border-gray-700 mb-6" />

    <!-- ── Call to action — penutup yang mengajak kontak ────────
         Ditampilkan di tengah, warna accent, bergaya undangan kolaborasi
         ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
    <p class="text-center text-primary font-semibold leading-relaxed">
        If you're looking for a QA engineer, project manager, or someone who does both —<br />
        let's talk.
    </p>

</article>
